data.description:
Discover this charming end unit townhome nestled within the highly sought-after Cherry Creek School District, boasting convenient access to shopping, dining, and entertainment just minutes away. Meticulously updated and renovated, this property awaits its new owners with a fresh appeal. Enjoy the convenience of two reserved parking spots directly in front of the unit, while recent HOA-maintained upgrades include a new roof, gutters, and exterior paint. Step into the heart of the home, Cozy living room boast tons of natural light with skylights and vaulted ceilings, wood burning fireplace with new mantel and tile. The dining area exudes modern but warm and inviting with a large chandelier and a custom brick accent wall. A brand-new kitchen bringing modern elegance with soft-close cabinets, open shelving, and a deep stainless-steel sink. Adorned with subway-style backsplash tile, the kitchen is both functional and stylish. New waterproof vinyl plank flooring flows seamlessly throughout the space, complemented by freshly painted walls, baseboards, door hardware and floor registers. Indulge in the luxurious bathroom featuring a custom shower door and a real wood countertop. Experience a heightened sense of privacy with new blinds and shades at every window. Large bedroom with new luxury plush carpet leads to an outside fenced patio yard. The private yard is ideal for summer gatherings and leisurely evenings outdoors. Don't miss the opportunity to make this meticulously updated townhome your own retreat within a vibrant community. Completely Renovated Brand New Town home new flooring, paint, cabinets, light fixtures, all new stainless-steel appliances, outlets all replaced and much more! (portion of patio and fence new).

Buyer and buyer's agent to verify all information.
